| Detail | Info |
|--------|------|
| **Format** | 60 multiple-choice questions, scenario-based |
| **Duration** | 120 minutes, proctored via ProctorFree |
| **Passing score** | 720 out of 1000 |
| **Attempts** | One attempt per registration |
